text: Jason Clarke (born 17 July 1969) is an Australian actor. Clarke is known for playing Tommy Caffee on the television series Brotherhood. He has also appeared in many movies such as Death Race (2008), Public Enemies (2009), Zero Dark Thirty (2013), White House Down (2013), Dawn of the Planet of the Apes (2014), Terminator Genisys (2015), Everest (2015), Chappaquiddick (2017), and Oppenheimer (2023). ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Australian movie actors Category:Australian television actors Category:Australian voice actors Category:Actors from Queensland
